---
// About.astro - Short intro about me and why this program exists
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Why I Created This Program
        </h2>
        <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-blue-600 mx-auto"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            After 15 years in tech, I've seen countless talented professionals get stuck in their careers.
            They have the skills but lack the strategic guidance and accountability to break through to the next level.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Traditional career advice is generic and outdated. You need personalized strategies that work
            for your unique situation, industry, and goals. That's exactly what this program provides.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-600">
            <p class="text-gray-800 font-medium italic">
              "The best investment you can make is in yourself. Personal mentorship accelerates growth
              in ways that no course or book ever could."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What You'll Get</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Personalized career roadmap and action plan</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Weekly accountability and progress tracking</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Industry insights and networking opportunities</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
